passages = ["The morning sun cast long shadows across the garden as Sarah walked along the winding path. Birds chirped melodiously in the trees above, their songs echoing through the quiet neighborhood. She breathed in the fresh air, feeling a sense of peace wash over her as she observed the vibrant flowers blooming in every direction.",

"Technology has transformed the way we communicate with one another. Email, instant messaging, and video calls have made staying connected easier than ever before. However, some argue that this constant connectivity has reduced our ability to engage in meaningful face-to-face interactions. Finding balance between digital and personal communication remains a challenge.",

"The old bookstore on Fifth Avenue had been family-owned for three generations. Its creaky wooden floors and towering shelves filled with thousands of volumes attracted book lovers from across the city. Every corner held hidden treasures waiting to be discovered by curious readers seeking their next great adventure.",

"Climate change poses unprecedented challenges for our planet and future generations. Rising temperatures are causing polar ice caps to melt, sea levels to rise, and extreme weather events to become more frequent. Scientists worldwide agree that immediate action is necessary to reduce carbon emissions and transition to renewable energy sources.",

"Learning a new language opens doors to different cultures and perspectives. It requires dedication, practice, and patience to master grammar, vocabulary, and pronunciation. The rewards, however, are invaluable—gaining the ability to connect with millions of speakers and experiencing the world through a fresh linguistic lens."]
